### Primary value proposition

> OSH gives users the flexibility of wireless smart-home sensors with the simplicity of a dedicated thermostat.

### Alternative version

> Get the temperature control you would normally build with sensors, gateways and automations — in one purpose-built thermostat.

### Consumer-focused version

